metadata.name: Rutin
metadata.description:
What is inside an artist? Is it different from other people? To understand an artist, is it necessary to look inside? Or do we have to understand? I don't know!

Technical Description and Story:

I had this X-Ray image taken in the radiology department of a hospital. I asked while doing this and I did it without removing my earrings. Because these earrings are one of the objects that represent me.

Size: 879x703 px, 96 dpi, JPEG
